---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout locale="en" title="About ClosersMatch — Mission, Vision & Approach" description="ClosersMatch is the platform connecting ambitious sales professionals with companies ready to grow. Technology, training, AI, and human expertise for better matches and measurable results.">

  <!-- ================================================
       HERO
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="oo-hero">
    <div class="container oo-hero__inner">
      <div class="oo-hero__content">
        <span class="label label--red">About us</span>
        <h1 class="oo-hero__title">
          We build the commercial<br />
          <span class="oo-hero__title-red">infrastructure companies<br />need to grow.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="oo-hero__subtitle">
          ClosersMatch is a performance-driven ecosystem that connects ambitious sales professionals with companies ready to scale. We combine technology, training, AI, and human expertise to deliver better matches, better performance, and measurable results.
        </p>
        <div class="oo-hero__trust-pills">
          <span class="trust-pill">✓ 50+ successful matches</span>
          <span class="trust-pill">✓ No cure no pay</span>
          <span class="trust-pill">✓ Results from week one</span>
        </div>
        <div class="oo-hero__actions">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--red btn--lg">Book your free intake →</a>
          <a href="#waarom-we-bestaan" class="btn btn--outline-dark-mode">Our story</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="oo-hero__visual">
        <div class="oo-hero__metrics-card">
          <div class="oo-metric">
            <span class="oo-metric__num">50+</span>
            <span class="oo-metric__label">Successful matches delivered</span>
          </div>
          <div class="oo-metric-divider"></div>
          <div class="oo-metric">
            <span class="oo-metric__num">€50K</span>
            <span class="oo-metric__label">Deal closed in week one, DetachPro</span>
          </div>
          <div class="oo-metric-divider"></div>
          <div class="oo-metric">
            <span class="oo-metric__num">48u</span>
            <span class="oo-metric__label">Average time to first match</span>
          </div>
          <div class="oo-metric-divider"></div>
          <div class="oo-hero__card-footer">
            <span>Founded to reshape the fragmented sales landscape</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       MISSIE & VISIE
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section oo-mv">
    <div class="container oo-mv__inner">
      <div class="oo-mv__col">
        <span class="label">Our mission</span>
        <h2 class="h2 oo-mv__title">Every company deserves<br />a reliable<br />sales team.</h2>
        <p class="oo-mv__body">The commercial market is broken. Companies pay for salespeople who do not perform. Sales professionals work for companies that do not use their talent. Both sides lose.</p>
        <p class="oo-mv__body">ClosersMatch changes that. By connecting companies with proven professionals through a system built on one principle: pay only for results.</p>
        <div class="oo-mv__quote">
          <blockquote>"We believe commercial success should not be a matter of luck. It is a system. And we are building that system."</blockquote>
          <cite>Founder, ClosersMatch</cite>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="oo-mv__col">
        <span class="label">Our vision</span>
        <h2 class="h2 oo-mv__title">The future of sales<br />is about networks,<br /><span class="oo-mv__title-red">not résumés.</span></h2>
        <p class="oo-mv__body">Traditional hiring models are outdated. The sales market does not need more job boards or CV databases. What it needs is a performance-driven ecosystem where companies and professionals connect based on track record, industry knowledge, and proven results.</p>
        <p class="oo-mv__body">That is exactly what ClosersMatch is building. A network of certified professionals, vetted companies, and a matching system built on results, not assumptions.</p>
        <div class="oo-mv__vision-pills">
          <span class="oo-vision-pill">Network over résumé</span>
          <span class="oo-vision-pill">Performance over promise</span>
          <span class="oo-vision-pill">Results over risk</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       WAAROM WE BESTAAN
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section oo-waarom" id="waarom-we-bestaan">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="oo-waarom__inner">
        <div class="oo-waarom__header">
          <span class="label">Why ClosersMatch exists</span>
          <h2 class="h2 oo-waarom__title">Two markets, one problem.<br /><span class="oo-waarom__title-red">ClosersMatch is the solution.</span></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="oo-waarom__content">
          <div class="oo-problem-block">
            <div class="oo-problem-block__icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="oo-problem-block__title">The problem for companies</h3>
              <p class="oo-problem-block__text">Companies spend months recruiting, onboarding, and training salespeople with no guarantee of results. They pay fixed salaries regardless of performance, carry employer risk, and lack visibility into commercial activity. The market is fragmented: freelancers are unreliable, recruiters are expensive, and internal teams are hard to scale.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="oo-problem-block">
            <div class="oo-problem-block__icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="oo-problem-block__title">The problem for sales professionals</h3>
              <p class="oo-problem-block__text">Ambitious salespeople struggle to find good opportunities. They work on platforms without quality leads, for companies with poor commission structures, or see their talent wasted on cold calling and admin. There is no clear growth path, no system for performance tracking, and no network to help them advance.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="oo-solution-block">
            <div class="oo-solution-block__label">The ClosersMatch approach</div>
            <p class="oo-solution-block__text">ClosersMatch was founded to solve both problems at once. By bringing companies, lead generators, and sales professionals together in one performance-driven ecosystem, built on transparency, certification, and shared success. No fixed salary. No recruitment fees. No risk. Only results.</p>
            <div class="oo-solution-block__stats">
              <div class="oo-sol-stat">
                <span class="oo-sol-stat__num">€50K+</span>
                <span class="oo-sol-stat__label">Deals closed through our platform</span>
              </div>
              <div class="oo-sol-stat">
                <span class="oo-sol-stat__num">Week 1</span>
                <span class="oo-sol-stat__label">Average time to first visible results</span>
              </div>
              <div class="oo-sol-stat">
                <span class="oo-sol-stat__num">100%</span>
                <span class="oo-sol-stat__label">No cure no pay model</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       TWEE DOELGROEPEN
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section oo-doelgroepen">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="oo-doelgroepen__header">
        <span class="label">Who we serve</span>
        <h2 class="h2 oo-doelgroepen__title">Two audiences.<br />One ecosystem.</h2>
        <p class="oo-doelgroepen__sub">ClosersMatch creates value on both sides of the commercial market and ensures they strengthen each other.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="oo-doelgroepen__grid">

        <div class="oo-doel-card">
          <div class="oo-doel-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="oo-doel-card__title">For businesses</h3>
          <p class="oo-doel-card__body">Scale your sales process without permanent headcount. Get direct access to certified closers and appointment setters, and pay only when there are results.</p>
          <ul class="oo-doel-card__list">
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Access to a network of certified professionals
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              No hiring risk, pay only for results
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Match within 48 hours, ready to deploy
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Predictable revenue processes and full CRM visibility
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Scalable without payroll costs or contract risk
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/for-businesses" class="btn btn--red oo-doel-card__cta">Explore for businesses →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="oo-doel-card oo-doel-card--dark">
          <div class="oo-doel-card__icon oo-doel-card__icon--light">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="oo-doel-card__title oo-doel-card__title--light">For sales professionals</h3>
          <p class="oo-doel-card__body oo-doel-card__body--light">Build a sustainable career in sales. Receive CM Certified training, work for vetted companies, and close deals that fit your style and industry.</p>
          <ul class="oo-doel-card__list oo-doel-card__list--light">
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Intensive CM Certified sales training
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Access to vetted companies with warm leads
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Personal guidance from experienced coaches
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Performance insight via dashboard and conversation analysis
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Build a long-term career in a growing network
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/for-closers" class="btn btn--outline-light oo-doel-card__cta">Explore for closers →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       DE CLOSERSMATCH STANDAARD
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section oo-standaard">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="oo-standaard__header">
        <span class="label label--red">What we stand for</span>
        <h2 class="h2 oo-standaard__title">The ClosersMatch standard.</h2>
        <p class="oo-standaard__sub">Every company is vetted. Every opportunity is evaluated. Every professional is certified. These are the five pillars our ecosystem is built on.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="oo-standaard__grid">

        <div class="oo-std-card">
          <div class="oo-std-card__icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="oo-std-card__title">Professionalism</h3>
          <p class="oo-std-card__text">We work exclusively with certified professionals and vetted companies. No compromises on quality. Every match is built on proven competence.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="oo-std-card">
          <div class="oo-std-card__icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="oo-std-card__title">Performance</h3>
          <p class="oo-std-card__text">Results are the only currency that counts. Our no cure no pay model ensures everyone in the ecosystem is driven by performance, not presence.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="oo-std-card">
          <div class="oo-std-card__icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="oo-std-card__title">Transparency</h3>
          <p class="oo-std-card__text">Full visibility for all parties. Companies see their pipeline in real time. Professionals see their performance and earnings. No hidden costs, no surprises.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="oo-std-card">
          <div class="oo-std-card__icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="oo-std-card__title">Accountability</h3>
          <p class="oo-std-card__text">We take responsibility for every match. If a professional underperforms, we find a solution. If a company does not honor its commitments, our team steps in.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="oo-std-card oo-std-card--featured">
          <div class="oo-std-card__icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="oo-std-card__title">Long-term partnerships</h3>
          <p class="oo-std-card__text">We are not a transactional platform. We build lasting relationships between companies and professionals, based on trust, growth, and shared long-term success.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       OPRICHTER / TEAM
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section oo-team">
    <div class="container oo-team__inner">
      <div class="oo-team__content">
        <span class="label">The team behind ClosersMatch</span>
        <h2 class="h2 oo-team__title">Built by people<br />who know the sales market<br /><span class="oo-team__title-red">from the inside.</span></h2>
        <p class="oo-team__body">ClosersMatch was founded by a team with years of experience in sales, recruitment, and technology. We have felt the frustrations on both sides, as entrepreneurs searching for salespeople and as salespeople searching for quality opportunities.</p>
        <p class="oo-team__body">Those frustrations were the starting point. The problem was too big to ignore: a fragmented market, no standard for quality, no system for performance tracking. So we built ClosersMatch.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--red btn--lg oo-team__cta">Meet our team →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="oo-team__cards">
        <div class="oo-founder-card">
          <div class="oo-founder-card__avatar">CM</div>
          <div class="oo-founder-card__info">
            <strong>ClosersMatch</strong>
            <span>Founded to reshape the sales market</span>
          </div>
          <div class="oo-founder-card__mission">
            <p>"We believe commercial success is not a matter of luck. It is a system, and we make that system better every day."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="oo-founder-card__facts">
            <div class="oo-founder-fact">
              <span class="oo-founder-fact__val">2024</span>
              <span class="oo-founder-fact__label">Founded</span>
            </div>
            <div class="oo-founder-fact">
              <span class="oo-founder-fact__val">NL</span>
              <span class="oo-founder-fact__label">Based in the Netherlands</span>
            </div>
            <div class="oo-founder-fact">
              <span class="oo-founder-fact__val">B2B</span>
              <span class="oo-founder-fact__label">Focus on high-ticket sales</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="oo-team-values">
          <div class="oo-team-value">
            <div class="oo-team-value__dot"></div>
            <span>Sales is a profession, not a side job</span>
          </div>
          <div class="oo-team-value">
            <div class="oo-team-value__dot"></div>
            <span>Results above all, always</span>
          </div>
          <div class="oo-team-value">
            <div class="oo-team-value__dot"></div>
            <span>Technology as an amplifier of human talent</span>
          </div>
          <div class="oo-team-value">
            <div class="oo-team-value__dot"></div>
            <span>Transparency in everything we do</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       AFSLUITENDE CTA
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="oo-closing">
    <div class="oo-closing__inner">
      <span class="label label--ghost-light">Free intake, no obligations</span>
      <h2 class="oo-closing__title">
        Ready to grow<br />commercially together?
      </h2>
      <p class="oo-closing__body">
        Whether you are a company ready to scale or a sales professional who wants to excel, ClosersMatch is the ecosystem that accelerates your growth.<br /><br />
        Book a free intake and discover in 30 minutes what ClosersMatch can do for you.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--red btn--xl oo-closing__btn">Book your free intake →</a>
      <p class="oo-closing__sub">No upfront costs. No obligations. Just a clear picture of your opportunities.</p>
      <p class="oo-closing__brand">ClosersMatch. <span>The Revenue Ecosystem.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ====================================================
     HERO
  ==================================================== */
  .oo-hero {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 162px 0 80px;
  }

  .oo-hero__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .oo-hero__content .label--red {
    background: rgba(221,52,46,0.1);
    color: var(--color-red);
    border: 1px solid rgba(221,52,46,0.25);
  }

  .oo-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-black);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 20px 0 24px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .oo-hero__title-red { color: var(--color-red); }

  .oo-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #4B5563;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .oo-hero__trust-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .trust-pill {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-black);
    background: var(--color-gray-light);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .oo-hero__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .oo-hero__metrics-card {
    background: var(--color-black);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 36px 32px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .oo-metric {
    padding: 20px 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .oo-metric__num {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .oo-metric__label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .oo-metric-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  .oo-hero__card-footer {
    padding-top: 20px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .oo-hero__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .oo-hero { padding: 100px 0 60px; }
    .oo-hero__actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
    .oo-hero__actions .btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
  }

  /* ====================================================
     MISSIE & VISIE
  ==================================================== */
  .oo-mv { background: #F9FAFB; }

  .oo-mv__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .oo-mv__title {
    margin-top: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .oo-mv__title-red { color: var(--color-red); }

  .oo-mv__body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .oo-mv__quote {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-border);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-red);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .oo-mv__quote blockquote {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-black);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .oo-mv__quote cite {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-mid);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .oo-mv__vision-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  .oo-vision-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-black);
    padding: 10px 18px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .oo-vision-pill::before {
